name: reflection of life
description: presenting what I feel and pouring it out. reflect on life. how beautiful is life? no, all we feel is how annoying life is. happiness, sadness, anxiety, and fear of death. Yes, life sucks when you think about it deeply. only achieve what we want, do good, do evil, and what else after that? only death awaits us. thanks for reading it. I give this work the title "reflection of life"
